            <h3 data-uuid="9decf478640a49ceab88629a496f911f">Part 2: Write an Informative Essay</h3>
            <h6 data-uuid="8f860994db074cec90de0160f92ca9ba">Historical Context</h6>
            <p data-uuid="2e0569256b844d0e915cbfda16468734"></p>
            <p data-uuid="697427b9317e44e1b4310b910633524c">Following the stock market crash in 1929,
                the economy fell into a depression. Banks failed and businesses closed. Millions
                of workers lost their jobs. Making matters worse, a severe drought hit in the
                1930s. Unable to grow crops, farmers across the Great Plains lost their land.</p>
            <h6 data-uuid="4da0e714fdc9455eaa9c7687cfcfcaac">Task</h6>
            <p data-uuid="8e7df474b31d41a5989f67936da0e7d2"></p>
            <p data-uuid="29b62cbb3bed47ee9ca35294f467940f">The Great Depression spread poverty across
                the country. Americans struggled to cope with the effects of dust storms and
                the economic collapse. Write an informative essay in which you describe the
                hardships facing Americans in the 1930s, as well as the governmentâ€™s efforts to
                help.</p>
            <p data-uuid="ddd9c4d009914b429e53c3c9e837fe6f">Complete the following steps as you plan
                and compose your essay.</p>
            <ol data-uuid="801e632964484c8685a6306245d54a40">
                <li data-uuid="95e508828dd94bf78591ce37391f57a1">Review your
                    notes and sources before you start writing.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="f46ec936f5bb441e8575cdc112254727">Use at
                    least <i>two</i> of the sources in Part 1, and develop the topic with relevant,
                    well-chosen text or visual evidence from the documents.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="b3ce98f3da39415895c56b9075df2d5a">Cite
                    specific text or visual evidence from each of the sources in your response.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="d57c935d74d94508ac8810398d6ad036">Plan your
                    essay so that it includes an introduction, several body paragraphs, and a
                    concluding paragraph.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="f7607df70cb34cd183a3c3f7e0e40030">Organize
                    your essay in a clear and logical way that focuses on the topic and supports it with
                    explanations and facts.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="e516d3aece8b4ebf9e2e02ec7c414044">Write a conclusion that sums up your ideas and
                    supports the information you present.</li>
            </ol>
